responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "54952FB74154B06FC277A3BCC859632A", "The seeds of judgement grow upon Daragal Estates and shall consume this land. I cannot stop this. You must do what I cannot. From a shard of the altar, my hands crafted the blade. In the wrong hands it reaped all life on my land, but in rightious hands it could have redeemed the past. ")
